OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening but with a
OL,7,Ffreshening southeast wind. Staying dry
OL,8,Ffor Shetland overnight, but clouding
OL,9,Fover with the odd spot of rain
OL,10,Fpossible for Orkney.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FMostly dry to start but
OL,13,Fcloud and rain will soon push north
OL,14,Fthrough the morning. Staying cloudy
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain and strong
OL,16,Fsoutheast winds throughout the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
