OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright spells and scattered showers
OL,7,Fduring Thursday. A dry start Friday
OL,8,Fwith rain pushing northeast later.
OL,9,FShowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
